  "original_title": "\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bcd - \u0b90\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sajid Prime Minister if Dulles becomes President - United People's Power",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ranjitmathumbandara has said that Sajith Premadasa will be chosen as the Prime Minister if Dulles is elected as the president of the unit.",
        "Ranjith Mathumabandara said that this will happen based on the agreement reached between the two.",
        "Ranjith Mathumabandara also said that Dulles unit boss has enough support to be elected as president."
      ],
